Usage: create_ccopt_preferred_cell_stripe [-help] -bbox <bbox> -cells <cells>
                                          -name <name>

-help            # Prints out the command usage
-bbox <bbox>     # the area in which all matching cells should be
                 # preferentially placed (string, required)
-cells <cells>   # cells that should be preferentially placed in this stripe
                 # (string, required)
-name <name>     # user-defined identifier for this preferred cell stripe
                 # (string, required)